---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Daniel Gierach | Sales & Marketing Executive | Ray White Collective"
  description="Daniel Gierach, Brisbane-born property professional at Ray White Collective. Degree in Property Economics, 10+ years across residential sales, marketing, business operations and construction."
>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">
  <div style="background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <img src="/img/daniel-headshot-tight.jpg" alt="Daniel Gierach"
        style="width:160px;height:160px;border-radius:18px;object-fit:cover;border:1.5px solid rgba(197,160,60,0.5);box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);margin-bottom:1.5rem;" />
      <span style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.58rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.55);margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Service beyond the transaction &middot; Value beyond expectation
      </span>
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3rem);font-weight:400;color:#f0ece4;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-bottom:0.55rem;">
        Daniel Gierach
      </h1>
      <span style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#f5d07a;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Sales &amp; Marketing Executive &middot; Ray White Collective</span>

      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1.25rem 2rem;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.82);">
        <a href="tel:+61412523821" data-cta="team_daniel_call" style="color:#f5d07a;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.37 1.9.72 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.35 1.85.59 2.81.72A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
          0412 523 821
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:daniel.gierach@raywhite.com" data-cta="team_daniel_email" style="color:#f5d07a;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          daniel.gierach@raywhite.com
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/dgierach/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-cta="team_daniel_instagram" style="color:#f5d07a;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"/></svg>
          @dgierach
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="padding:3rem 0 6rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8" style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);line-height:1.9;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;">

      <p>Born and raised in Brisbane, Daniel has dedicated his career to the property industry, completing a degree in Property Economics and gaining over a decade of experience across residential sales, marketing, business operations, and construction.</p>

      <p>Daniel specialises in helping clients effectively market their properties, combining strategic insight with tailored campaigns that maximise exposure and attract the right buyers. With a background spanning business development, recruitment, and marketing, he brings a unique understanding of how to position properties for strong results, whether it's a family home, investment property or development site.</p>

      <p>His work is grounded in data, detail and clear communication, ensuring clients feel confident and well-informed throughout the sales process. Daniel works across Brisbane's high-demand suburbs and is passionate about showcasing the true potential of every property he works with.</p>

      <p>He believes real estate is about more than just transactions; it's about creating standout campaigns and meaningful conversations that lead to exceptional outcomes.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:2rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.1);">
        <a href="/your-team" style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-gold);text-decoration:none;">&larr; Back to your team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

</Layout>
